	Fellow AMOS people
I am trying to output long sam files. (From CDTV) and I cannot for the
life of me get the demo on page 8.2.7 to work.
Below is my modded version. Could someone try it and see if they also
miss the first section of the SVX file.

(ASC file BELOW)

   Reserve As Chip Work 10,10000
   Reserve As Chip Work 11,10000
   Open In 1,"eng:sc/e/12.E"
   
   
   A$=Input$(1,12)
   If(Left$(A$,4)="FORM") and(Right$(A$,4)="8SVX")
      Do 
         A$=Input$(1,8)
         PCHUNK=Pof(1) : LCHUNK=Leek(Varptr(A$)+4)
         If Left$(A$,4)="VHDR"
            B$=Input$(1,LCHUNK) : A=Varptr(B$)
            CULEN=Leek(A)+Leek(A+4)
            CUFREQ=Deek(A+12)
            LCHUNK=0
         End If 
         If Left$(A$,4)="NAME"
            B$=Input$(1,LCHUNK) : CUNAME$=""
            For N=1 To 8
               C$=Mid$(B$,N,1) : If(C$<" ") or(C$>Chr$(127)) : C$=" " : End If 
               CUNAME$=CUNAME$+C$
            Next 
            LCHUNK=0
         End If 
         If Left$(A$,4)="BODY"
            Exit 
         End If 
         If LCHUNK : Pof(1)=PCHUNK+LCHUNK : End If 
      Loop 
   Else 
      Boom : Wait Key : Edit 
   End If 
   
   L=CULEN : C=0 : A=Start(10) : B=Start(11)
   
   Sload 1 To Start(10),10000 : C=C+10000
   Sload 1 To Start(11),10000 : C=C+10000
   
   Led Off 
   Sam Raw 15,Start(10),10000,CUFREQ
   Do 
      Gosub CHECK_SAM
      If C>L Then Goto FIN
      Sam Swap 15 To Start(11),10000
      Sload 1 To Start(10),10000 : C=C+10000
      Gosub CHECK_SAM
      If C>L Then Goto FIN
      Sam Swap 15 To Start(10),10000
      Sload 1 To Start(11),10000 : C=C+10000
   Loop 
   
   CHECK_SAM:
   Repeat 
      Z=Sam Swapped(0)
      Locate 5,5 : Print Z;" "
   Until Z
   Return 
   
   FIN: Close 1 : Sam Stop : Led On 
   Edit 


Thanks in advance

